{
  "stem": "280.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were very young, we all lived in the same house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not for long, because my oldest brother married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was quite a bit of difference between my older brother and myself, as I-- as I mentioned from two mothers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother lived in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a village in-- about three hours away by bus, because the train-- the train didn't go there, from Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were big landowners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They owned a tremendous amount of the land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a mill which-- which made flour, and an oil press, and oil, and they had orchards.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a big [GERMAN], as they call it the German, a big house, home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father was a city boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember the story, that he-- that I'll never forget because he mentioned it many times, that he never was in a village, and he couldn't imagine.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when he came to see his future wife, they picked him up in another small town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came by train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they picked him up with a beautiful carriage, with a beautiful horse-drawn carriage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he arrived in that village, and he saw that house, his smile remained open, because he thought the village is a village, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- so that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my childhood, the biggest treat was to spend some time in the summer in that village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my grandmother, and with numerous relatives, cousins, and aunts and uncles, it was the biggest treat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- so big orchards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- in the-- in the late summer, when they harvested the-- the fruits, the plums, and they made-- they had a-- like a-- like a room where they dried the prunes-- where they dried the plums, and they became prunes.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
